Best of 5 (Online)

* Grand final. BLUEJAYS will have a 1-0 map advantage due to coming from the upper bracket.

** Winner qualifies for ESL Challenger League Season 42.

*** The match was originally scheduled to be played on the 14th of July 2022, 13:00 CEST, however due to a last minute false positive ESEA ban for account sharing affecting one of the BLUEJAYS players (kyxsan), the 1st map was played by BLUEJAYS with their coach (Cr0n0s) and the match eventually ended as a forfeit win in favor of forZe. After reassessing the situation, the league organizer decided in favor of a complete rematch (from the default 1-0 in favor of BLUEJAYS) the following day (15th of July 2022, 13:00 CEST).

                  

                  

                    

                      
1. forZe removed Vertigo

                      
2. BLUEJAYS removed Nuke

                      
3. forZe picked Dust2

                      
4. BLUEJAYS picked Mirage

                      
5. forZe picked Overpass

                      
6. BLUEJAYS picked Inferno
